 is exhibited. However,\n$f\\approx \\mathcal{O}(10)$ when the couplings are smaller. Although not\nderivable from quasi-particles, our results at optimal doping fit a Drude-type\nphenomenology with Planckian scattering time, and an almost model-independent\n$n/m$, which is about $2\\pi$ times the Fermi liquid value at same $E_F$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-06"}
