le of 22 sources, we obtain\n$\\beta < 2.89$ and $\\beta < 3.53$ in the high and low lensing models,\nrespectively. These constraints strongly disfavor steep QLF shapes previously\nproposed in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 21:41:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-21"}
