lation between heavy tails and\ngeneralization is not globally monotonic. (iii) We prove matching lower-bounds\non uniform stability, implying that our bounds are tight in terms of the\nheaviness of the tails. We support our theory with synthetic and real neural\nnetwork experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 19:59:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2022 22:01:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2023 07:22:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-14"}
