nsion and elaboration analogous to\norganic growth. Finally, we present an organicist interpretation of delaying\nthe climax: viewing musical form as the result of organic growth, the arrow of\ntime translates to a preference for prepending structure over appending\nstructure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 21:19:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-06"}
