ic region accessible to the\nlatter.\n  This work provides a pedagogical description of GPD evolution equations which\nbenefits from a renewed interest as future colliders, such as the electron-ion\ncolliders in the US and in China, are being designed. It also paves the way to\nthe extension of GPD evolution codes to higher accuracies in pQCD desirable for\nprecision phenomenology at these facilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jun 2022 06:52:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 13:37:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
