in's analysis on Du Val singularities through \\'etale local\nfundamental groups. The main results in the paper are also valid for\n$\\ell$-adic sheaves, mixed Hodge modules, and more generally motivic\n$\\infty$-categories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jun 2022 13:37:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-06"}
